# pkit-owned — rendered wholesale by `pkit install` / `pkit sync` from each
# installed component's `runtime_ignore:` declaration (ADR-009 Amendment 1).
# DO NOT EDIT: regenerated from scratch every run; hand edits are overwritten.
# An uninstalled component's lines are simply absent on the next render.

**/__pycache__/
permissions/project/diagnose.yaml
permissions/project/diagnose-log.jsonl
permissions/project/sandbox-provenance.yaml
permissions/project/active-profile.yaml
capabilities/project-management/project/process/**/*.journal.jsonl
capabilities/project-management/project/instance/*.json
